What services does a digital marketing agency provide?
Search Engine Optimization (SEO): Enhances your website's visibility on search engines like Google, aiming to increase organic (non-paid) traffic by optimizing content, keywords, and site structure.

Social Media Management: Strategically manages your presence on social media platforms (e.g., Facebook, Instagram, Twitter) to build brand awareness, engage with your audience, and drive traffic to your website.

Pay-Per-Click (PPC) Advertising: Creates targeted ads that appear in search engine results or on websites and charges you only when someone clicks on them, effectively driving immediate traffic to your site.
Website Design and Development: Designs and builds professional and user-friendly websites optimized for both search engines and user experience to enhance brand credibility and drive conversions.

